Key Match Events: Shreyas Iyer and K.L. Rahul scored centuries.
Mohammed Siraj took the wicket of Sybrand Engelbrecht.
Post-Match Reflections: India finished its World Cup league engagements with nine wins on the trot.
India will take on New Zealand in the semifinal at Mumbai on Wednesday.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match took place at the M. Chinnaswamy Stadium in Bengaluru on November 12, 2023.
The Diwali weekend spirit was in vogue at the stadium.
